pageContext.claim: “.@SeanParnellUSA is a SUPERSTAR running against a Lamb, to be exact, a weak puppet of crazy Nancy Pelosi!”
pageContext.analysis: Rep. Connor Lamm (D-Penn.) as a “puppet” for Pelosi is a tough sell. In his first session of Congress, he voted with the president more than he voted against him. Overall, he votes with Trump nearly 25 percent of the time, according to FiveThirtyEight’s calculations.
